title: Las Vegas
description: Sin City, Entertainment Capital of the World, The Strip, whatever you call it there's no denying Las Vegas is the Mecca of bachelor(ette) parties.

title: Austin
description: With a city slogan like “Keep Austin Weird,” Austin is like the cool kid who doesn’t give any fucks

title: Montreal
description: There may not be a better city in the world for a bachelor(ette) party. You’ll be hard pressed to find someone who’s been there and had a bad time. After all, Montreal has amazing food, nightlife and beautiful looking people. Oh, and did we mention extremely affordable thanks to a strong US dollar compared to the monopoly money they use up north.
